{
  "id": "2023-06-15_screen_english",
  "date": "2023-06-15",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "리틀 이탈리아 (Little Italy)",
  "duration_sec": 918.04,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2023-06-15_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.38,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 즐거운 아침에 스크린 잉글리시 함께합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 4.38,
      "end": 8.04,
      "text": "로미오 둘, 줄리엣 둘"
    },
    {
      "start": 8.04,
      "end": 11.16,
      "text": "이렇게 둘둘이 등장을 하는 셈과 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 11.16,
      "end": 13.98,
      "text": "프랑카, 카를로 커플이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.98,
      "end": 16.84,
      "text": "또 니키하고 레오는 사실은"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.84,
      "end": 18.68,
      "text": "They're not a couple yet 이긴 하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 18.68,
      "end": 19.1,
      "text": "Not official"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.1,
      "end": 20.42,
      "text": "어, 그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.42,
      "end": 24.2,
      "text": "네, 아마 이제 조만간 되지 않을까라고 예상을 해보고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.2,
      "end": 24.92,
      "text": "아, 될 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.92,
      "end": 30.42,
      "text": "Anyway, traditional pizza가 아마도 is the best 이겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.7,
      "end": 32.12,
      "text": "Do you like traditional pizza?"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.26,
      "end": 32.88,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.88,
      "end": 34.48,
      "text": "아, you went to Italy"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.48,
      "end": 34.76,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.76,
      "end": 36.98,
      "text": "You're a Italy honeymooner"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.98,
      "end": 39.76,
      "text": "맞습니다. 우리 또 공통점이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.76,
      "end": 42.66,
      "text": "Yes! 이탈리아 신혼여행 동기"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.66,
      "end": 45.56,
      "text": "I love the traditional pizza I tried there"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.56,
      "end": 50.32,
      "text": "Yeah, 이렇게 전통적인 pizza가 무엇보다도 최고이기는 하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.32,
      "end": 51.7,
      "text": "그럼에도 불구하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.7,
      "end": 55.24,
      "text": "There are a lot of fusion-style pizzas가 많이 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.24,
      "end": 56.42,
      "text": "So many"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.42,
      "end": 58.98,
      "text": "그래요, 그래서 우리가 주문을 하기 전에"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.98,
      "end": 62.8,
      "text": "솔직히 이런 다양한 메뉴들 때문에 고민을 하게 되잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.8,
      "end": 66.32,
      "text": "저는 가끔 I order seafood pizza"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.32,
      "end": 68.22,
      "text": "이런 것도 주문을 해보긴 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.22,
      "end": 72.92,
      "text": "Yeah, I never encountered a seafood pizza before I came to Korea"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.92,
      "end": 76.26,
      "text": "Korea has very different toppings than the U.S."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.5,
      "end": 78.06,
      "text": "Pepperoni"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.06,
      "end": 82.68,
      "text": "American kids, they always eat pepperoni or cheese"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.68,
      "end": 83.58,
      "text": "아, 그렇군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.58,
      "end": 84.54,
      "text": "두 가지부터 먹어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.54,
      "end": 86.92,
      "text": "When I was a kid, I liked vegetarian"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.92,
      "end": 88.34,
      "text": "I was a little weird"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.34,
      "end": 89.72,
      "text": "좀 이 맛이 좀 달라가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.72,
      "end": 91.84,
      "text": "I loved vegetarian pizza"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.84,
      "end": 93.7,
      "text": "because it had lots of toppings"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.7,
      "end": 95.7,
      "text": "But I never saw seafood"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.7,
      "end": 97.06,
      "text": "until I came here"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.06,
      "end": 97.8,
      "text": "그렇군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.8,
      "end": 99.56,
      "text": "Like shrimp, coconut shrimp pizza"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.56,
      "end": 101.32,
      "text": "sweet potatoes"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.32,
      "end": 102.38,
      "text": "그런 거 다 드셔보셨어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.48,
      "end": 103.12,
      "text": "다 보고 봤죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.12,
      "end": 104.3,
      "text": "So how did you like it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.58,
      "end": 105.26,
      "text": "I liked it"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.26,
      "end": 107.32,
      "text": "because I love all kinds of toppings"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.32,
      "end": 109.24,
      "text": "물론 호불호 갈리겠지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.24,
      "end": 111.3,
      "text": "저는 잘 안 가리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.3,
      "end": 112.56,
      "text": "맛있게 먹었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.56,
      "end": 112.96,
      "text": "좀 더"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.96,
      "end": 114.5,
      "text": "그러니까 성격도 좋으시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.5,
      "end": 116.12,
      "text": "입맛도 이렇게 좋으시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.12,
      "end": 117.74,
      "text": "그렇습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.74,
      "end": 118.4,
      "text": "맛이"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.4,
      "end": 120.3,
      "text": "You like the seafood"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.3,
      "end": 123.02,
      "text": "근데 이렇게 다양한 토핑들에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.02,
      "end": 124.52,
      "text": "좀 검색을 해봤거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.52,
      "end": 126.74,
      "text": "근데 진짜 종류가 많더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.74,
      "end": 128.78,
      "text": "Tomato, ketchup, and mustard"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.78,
      "end": 129.28,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.54,
      "end": 130.68,
      "text": "That's a hamburger"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.68,
      "end": 131.7,
      "text": "Yeah, 그리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.7,
      "end": 133.24,
      "text": "Ketchup and mustard go on hamburgers"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.24,
      "end": 135.08,
      "text": "And baked beans"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.08,
      "end": 137.0,
      "text": "그 다음에 chocolate"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.0,
      "end": 138.0,
      "text": "Chocolate"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.0,
      "end": 138.96,
      "text": "That's not a pizza"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.96,
      "end": 139.84,
      "text": "That's a dessert"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.84,
      "end": 140.4,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.4,
      "end": 141.34,
      "text": "디젤트 피자"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.34,
      "end": 141.64,
      "text": "그리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.64,
      "end": 143.62,
      "text": "Cold fish"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.62,
      "end": 146.26,
      "text": "아니, cold fish는 무슨 의미일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.5,
      "end": 148.4,
      "text": "If the fish is cold, is the pizza cold?"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.56,
      "end": 150.68,
      "text": "The pizza is hot and the fish is cold?"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.78,
      "end": 151.22,
      "text": "그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.22,
      "end": 152.08,
      "text": "아, 좋네"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.08,
      "end": 154.56,
      "text": "Coconut, 아까 말씀하신 것처럼 이것도 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.56,
      "end": 155.3,
      "text": "그 다음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.3,
      "end": 156.3,
      "text": "Crocodile"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.3,
      "end": 157.58,
      "text": "Crocodile"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.58,
      "end": 160.12,
      "text": "그 다음에 emu and kangaroo"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.12,
      "end": 162.52,
      "text": "Where did you get these pizzas?"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.94,
      "end": 164.28,
      "text": "아마도 이게 호주에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.28,
      "end": 166.66,
      "text": "뭔가 이런 특징을 담아가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.66,
      "end": 168.86,
      "text": "그 모양으로 만드는 게 아닐까라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.86,
      "end": 169.9,
      "text": "추측은 하고 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.9,
      "end": 170.84,
      "text": "From down under"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.84,
      "end": 171.3,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.3,
      "end": 171.96,
      "text": "Hey, mate"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.96,
      "end": 173.94,
      "text": "We put kangaroos on our pizzas"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.94,
      "end": 176.48,
      "text": "And what about smoked reindeer?"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.9,
      "end": 177.24,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.24,
      "end": 178.04,
      "text": "잔인하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.04,
      "end": 180.08,
      "text": "I went to Finland once"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.08,
      "end": 181.3,
      "text": "I had reindeer"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.3,
      "end": 182.72,
      "text": "Beautiful reindeer"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.72,
      "end": 183.96,
      "text": "With salmon"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.96,
      "end": 185.56,
      "text": "But not on pizza"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.56,
      "end": 187.02,
      "text": "Like steak"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.02,
      "end": 187.94,
      "text": "이렇게 칼질하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.94,
      "end": 188.6,
      "text": "먹었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.6,
      "end": 189.22,
      "text": "너무 맛있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.22,
      "end": 189.76,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.86,
      "end": 191.22,
      "text": "그거 피자 위에 올리기"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.22,
      "end": 191.92,
      "text": "너무 아까운데"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.92,
      "end": 192.64,
      "text": "아깝군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.64,
      "end": 193.42,
      "text": "그리고 한우"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.42,
      "end": 195.14,
      "text": "뭐 꽃등심급인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.14,
      "end": 196.96,
      "text": "한우 꽃등심 피자"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.96,
      "end": 198.02,
      "text": "그거 아깝잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.02,
      "end": 198.64,
      "text": "그쵸"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.64,
      "end": 199.2,
      "text": "그 다음"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.2,
      "end": 199.78,
      "text": "burgers"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.78,
      "end": 201.32,
      "text": "fries and chicken nuggets"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.32,
      "end": 202.48,
      "text": "이런 것들도 다"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.48,
      "end": 203.14,
      "text": "토핑으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.14,
      "end": 204.64,
      "text": "올리는 곳이 있다고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.64,
      "end": 205.92,
      "text": "Seafood"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.92,
      "end": 207.02,
      "text": "I'm okay with seafood"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.02,
      "end": 207.98,
      "text": "Sweet potato"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.98,
      "end": 209.26,
      "text": "Stuff like that"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.26,
      "end": 210.76,
      "text": "But some of these things"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.76,
      "end": 212.36,
      "text": "I honestly would prefer"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.36,
      "end": 213.46,
      "text": "just the basics"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.46,
      "end": 215.16,
      "text": "Stick to the basics"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.16,
      "end": 216.6,
      "text": "Great tomato sauce"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.6,
      "end": 217.82,
      "text": "Great crust"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.82,
      "end": 219.22,
      "text": "And good cheese"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.22,
      "end": 219.68,
      "text": "역시"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.68,
      "end": 221.94,
      "text": "이렇게 트래디셔널한 피자는"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.94,
      "end": 223.1,
      "text": "역시 매력이"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.1,
      "end": 224.54,
      "text": "끝없는 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.54,
      "end": 226.52,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 들어볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.52,
      "end": 228.14,
      "text": "One day I hope"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.14,
      "end": 228.8,
      "text": "something like this"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.8,
      "end": 229.64,
      "text": "could be my legacy"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.64,
      "end": 231.78,
      "text": "Like a pizza shop"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.78,
      "end": 232.42,
      "text": "on the bottom"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.42,
      "end": 233.26,
      "text": "organic garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.26,
      "end": 233.78,
      "text": "on top"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.78,
      "end": 234.74,
      "text": "I'll call it"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.74,
      "end": 235.5,
      "text": "Pizza Organica"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.5,
      "end": 236.76,
      "text": "I love it"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.76,
      "end": 238.22,
      "text": "Have you leased a space?"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.54,
      "end": 239.72,
      "text": "No, but I got my eye"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.72,
      "end": 240.24,
      "text": "on the spot"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.24,
      "end": 241.92,
      "text": "Still saving up though"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.92,
      "end": 243.28,
      "text": "Maybe when my dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.28,
      "end": 244.12,
      "text": "retires, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.8,
      "end": 246.06,
      "text": "Leo, why would you wait?"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.12,
      "end": 247.44,
      "text": "That could be in 20 years"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.44,
      "end": 249.36,
      "text": "What do you want me to do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.92,
      "end": 250.62,
      "text": "Compete with him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.45,
      "end": 252.41,
      "text": "How is it that I'm the one"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.41,
      "end": 253.33,
      "text": "in culinary school"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.33,
      "end": 254.33,
      "text": "and yet you're the one"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.33,
      "end": 255.31,
      "text": "coming up with the dishes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.31,
      "end": 257.94,
      "text": "So he's talking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.94,
      "end": 259.74,
      "text": "his future plans"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.74,
      "end": 260.84,
      "text": "이거 뭔가"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.84,
      "end": 261.64,
      "text": "특별한 의미가"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.64,
      "end": 262.44,
      "text": "있는 거 아닌가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.82,
      "end": 263.24,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.24,
      "end": 264.5,
      "text": "They're planning"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.5,
      "end": 265.32,
      "text": "They're talking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.32,
      "end": 266.86,
      "text": "the future together"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.86,
      "end": 268.92,
      "text": "She is leading him"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.92,
      "end": 270.42,
      "text": "in good directions"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.42,
      "end": 270.78,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.78,
      "end": 273.4,
      "text": "사실 we don't tell anyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.4,
      "end": 275.0,
      "text": "about our future plans"
    },
    {
